00:01:55.910 --> 00:01:58.220
and it piles us up
with a lot of bullshit.

00:01:58.220 --> 00:02:02.388
And then all of a sudden, we
think that we're somebody else,

00:02:02.388 --> 00:02:03.930
so we need to be
something different.

00:02:03.930 --> 00:02:06.160
