00:02:18.770 --> 00:02:20.760
And you realize how
much of an empty vessel

00:02:20.760 --> 00:02:22.400
these kids really are.

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:26.000
And we were once these same
empty vessels, and then slowly,

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:28.880
but surely, all the stuff
that society teaches us,

00:02:28.880 --> 00:02:31.810
our parents teach us, family
teaches us, media teaches us,

00:02:31.810 --> 00:02:33.470
it crystallizes in who we are.

00:02:33.470 --> 00:02:34.970
And then we start
to think that this

00:02:34.970 --> 00:02:36.560
was tattooed into
our soul, and this

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:38.150
is who we are the whole time.

00:02:38.150 --> 00:02:40.700
