not, and we can go back

00:02:40.700 --> 00:02:42.950
to a better essence
of who we were

00:02:42.950 --> 00:02:46.040
by not acquiring more
things, but instead, letting

00:02:46.040 --> 00:02:47.295
go of a lot of stuff.

00:02:47.295 --> 00:02:48.920
