where "Unlearn" was.

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:52.230
So when I was in my most
challenging time in life,

00:02:52.230 --> 00:02:54.830
I was searching for
that Tumblr quote

00:02:54.830 --> 00:02:57.770
or that idea that
was going to save me

00:02:57.770 --> 00:02:58.880
