00:05:10.670 --> 00:05:13.610
And I think for
me, what I realized

00:05:13.610 --> 00:05:16.730
is the things that
kind of tickle my fancy

00:05:16.730 --> 00:05:19.650
and get me excited are
stimulation and learning.

00:05:19.650 --> 00:05:21.500
I'm a lifelong learner.

00:05:21.500 --> 00:05:23.890
That doesn't necessarily
mean I was a great student.

00:05:23.890 --> 00:05:26.890
