00:07:51.340 --> 00:07:54.080
KANWER SINGH: The name was
purely born out of spite.

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:54.580
I was--

00:07:54.580 --> 00:07:54.840
TY WARD: I knew it.

00:07:54.840 --> 00:07:55.340
I knew it.

00:07:58.870 --> 00:08:01.600
KANWER SINGH: In Sikh
heritage and Sikh philosophy,

00:08:01.600 --> 00:08:05.350
the number one challenge
to your peace is your ego.

00:08:05.350 --> 00:08:08.680
And so when I was
on hip hop forums

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:12.820
and just participating on my
favorite outcast chat boards,

00:08:12.820 --> 00:08:15.320
my username was just
the word Humble.

00:08:15.320 --> 00:08:18.280
And then I got involved
in online rap battles,

00:08:18.280 --> 00:08:23.920
and then in a rap battle,
I had a line that said,

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:27.860
rappers are basic,
emcees are more advanced.

00:08:27.860 --> 00:08:30.280
But I'm even better,
I'm the poet.

00:08:30.280 --> 00:08:32.320
And it was just a cocky
line to kind of say

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:34.240
that I'm better than
these rappers and emcees.

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:36.100
I ended up winning this
really big tournament

00:08:36.100 --> 00:08:38.308
where I had to compete with
five, six different guys.

00:08:38.308 --> 00:08:40.985
And to rub it in, I changed
my name to Humble the Poet.

00:08:40.985 --> 00:08:42.210
TY WARD: Oh.

00:08:42.210 --> 00:08:44.323
You mean a time for the actual--

00:08:44.323 --> 00:08:45.865
did you win, and
then you changed it?

00:08:45.865 --> 00:08:47.280
KANWER SINGH: No, I
