00:08:47.280 --> 00:08:47.530
TY WARD: OK.

00:08:47.530 --> 00:08:48.905
KANWER SINGH: To
rub it in, yeah.

00:08:48.905 --> 00:08:49.880
So everybody knew.

00:08:49.880 --> 00:08:52.783
And years later, I'm
in a friend's basement.

00:08:52.783 --> 00:08:54.700
And we have a microphone
against the mattress.

00:08:54.700 --> 00:08:56.380
