that name's too long.

00:09:09.250 --> 00:09:10.200
You need a short name.

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:11.320
You need a one syllable name.

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:12.020
I'm like, you know what?

00:09:12.020 --> 00:09:12.815
Screw all you guys.

00:09:12.815 --> 00:09:14.440
I'm going to stick
with Humble the Poet

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:16.190
because you guys don't
think it will work.

00:09:16.190 --> 00:09:17.630
I'm going to make it work.

00:09:17.630 --> 00:09:20.320
And they were right
in some instances.

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:23.882
This was right before
social media tags and names.

00:09:23.882 --> 00:09:25.840
A shorter name would have
probably been better,

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:27.610
but now, I'm stuck with it.

00:09:27.610 --> 00:09:28.610
I'm stubborn.

00:09:28.610 --> 00:09:30.335
And it's not going anywhere.

00:09:30.335 --> 00:09:31.210
TY WARD: I like that.

