00:44:30.200 --> 00:44:33.920
You're not being encouraged to
isolate yourself from the world

00:44:33.920 --> 00:44:36.320
and sit in your room and
meditate all the time,

00:44:36.320 --> 00:44:41.570
and avoid challenges,
avoid temptation, and avoid

00:44:41.570 --> 00:44:42.800
