00:44:42.800 --> 00:44:44.900
You're encouraged to
be out in the world,

00:44:44.900 --> 00:44:50.430
and be assertive and
view things accordingly.

00:44:50.430 --> 00:44:53.600
So for me, I know
growing up, I probably

00:44:53.600 --> 00:44:57.380
connected much more with Malcolm
X than with Martin Luther King.

