always kind of viewed

00:45:16.400 --> 00:45:19.130
people-- that is a lot more
pragmatic in understanding

00:45:19.130 --> 00:45:22.970
that sometimes, when fighting
oppression, you have to fight.

00:45:22.970 --> 00:45:25.610
You can't simply sit in
or do a hunger strike.

00:45:25.610 --> 00:45:27.320
You have to actually fight.

00:45:27.320 --> 00:45:29.300
You have to speak up.

00:45:29.300 --> 00:45:33.650
And now in modern
sense, for me, that just

00:45:33.650 --> 00:45:35.900
